<!---

https://forum.shotcut.org/t/filter-set-fun-text-animation/41982

1920x1080 (30fps): Fun Text Animation 1 (2 secs)

Description:

A small set of two text animation options for your videos. The animation was created for video mode 1920x1080x30fps.
How to properly prepare clips:

Create a color object with the following parameters:

White color.
Duration 2 seconds.
How to install this effect:

Shotcut - Settings - App Data Directory - Show - filter-sets (unzip the contents of the archive into this folder).
Important Note:

Shotcut version 23.11.29 and higher is required, because filters work on new types of keyframes.
-->
